  "legend": "When a Captain thunders to war on a Space Marine bike, he can race to the most critical locations on the battlefield. He smashes foes aside, cuts down countless fleeing enemies, or joins his Outriders to carry out reconnaissance missions in person so as to best develop his battle plans with first-hand knowledge.",
